{"tid":1203790,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"各位請分享比其他父母 我好擔心啊","createTime":"2019-06-11T13:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T18:28:32.000Z","uid":912,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5e653354f6d498b91239540c369b7f32ba6b7e51","tid":1203790,"uid":912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JK2ngXw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJK2ngXw.png&h=477dceef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ik8cvW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ik8cvW.gif&h=333f3c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好擔心小朋友會學壞<br />\n我同佢講咗<br />\n唔好再同啲爸爸/媽媽做警察嘅同學仔做朋友<br />\n唔好再同佢地玩<br />\n<br />\n佢地啲爸爸媽媽連老人家都恰<br />\n啲小朋友係金鐘又被人亂搜身罰企<br />\n老師都唔會咁樣罰你企 係咪先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢啲同學仔都唔係好人黎！</span>"},{"pid":"59119b5fd9cbf642965dcef0fcbc2e565e1282b9","tid":1203790,"uid":912,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:28:39.000Z","msg":"真係好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家嘅仔女唔好被呢啲惡霸恰<br />\n唔好再同佢地玩！<br />\n<br />\n身為家長有責任要保護小朋友<br />\n唔好比佢地識到啲壞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20749e12c300ac6a861234911b3803f787122e1","tid":1203790,"uid":912,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:35:07.000Z","msg":"呢度竟然咁少家長<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25cbf89e54edc76c7b15eea809bfebef806ffe3","tid":1203790,"uid":912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:41:34.000Z","msg":"分享比其他父母親<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcee9d7122b662739b5e06af4b71e507cd0fd087","tid":1203790,"u